{
  "texts": [
    "Let me therefore turn to the way opacity challenges the legitimation of AI power.",
    "The natural opacity of AI systems poses a significant challenge to the sociological legitimacy of public decisionmaking.",
    "This is intuitive: How can we know if a decision is fair or good if we cannot know the reasoning behind it?",
    "If we have no intuitive understanding of the system that produced it?",
    "This intuition has been formalized into the idea that democratic legitimacy requires that reasoning behind decisions be made public."
  ]
}